description: The SLI Swiss Leader Index (TR) aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Swiss blue chip companies listed on the SIX Swiss Exchange 30 largest and most liquid companies Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Quarterly index review, with caps to ensure compliance with UCITS diversification laws Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.six-swiss-exchange.com
name: Xtrackers SLI UCITS ETF 1D
